{"tid":421480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港仲有有禮貌嘅老人家","createTime":"2017-10-02T09:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T10:13:53.000Z","uid":87639,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"494d8c23f19ff6e669c5fcf817c846065ddd5e55","tid":421480,"uid":87639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"搭緊西鐵見到3個老人家上車 2個啊婆1個啊伯 咁我諗住讓個位俾佢地坐 <br />\n因為啊伯拎住袋唔知乜 好似好重<br />\n之後個啊伯勁霸氣話唔洗 一個站就落車 我唔坐！<br />\n佢老婆就望住我 我仲好堅持話讓俾佢坐 <br />\n但個啊伯死都唔肯坐 我都諗住算啦<br />\n點知佢老婆係咁同我講sorry sorry唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實香港仲有少部分好嘅老人家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d51aa80e3793f569409f68b8d92251e3d0f5a0c","tid":421480,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T09:35:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"786689c4dcc5038a95b4c450c126de92507e6dab","tid":421480,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}